                     referred as Tǝgre Mač̣č̣ohyā ("Cry of <placeName ref="LOC5932Tegray"
                        >Tǝgray</placeName>"), the area where people from <placeName
                        ref="LOC5932Tegray">Tǝgray</placeName> camped when they came to <placeName
                        ref="LOC3577Gondar">Gondar</placeName> to appeal to the <roleName
                        type="function">emperor</roleName>.</ab>
